TC Kundi - Managing Partner and Investment Committee member - REAF, AREF and REAF II
Mr. Kundi is a co-founder of Berkeley Energy. He is a board member of the Berkeley Energy Limited, the holding company for the Berkeley Energy management group. TC Kundi is the Managing Partner, directing the firm's development since its incorporation, and is a member of both REAF and REAF II Investment Committee and is the Chairman of the AREF Investment Committee.He is also a board member for all REAF and AREF portfolio investments.TC Kundi also oversees Berkeley Energy India, Berkeley's subsidiary in New Delhi and Berkeley Energy Renewables Singapore, its subsidiary in Singapore which provide operational and administrative support to the manager of REAF. Mr. Kundi is one of a handful of professionals globally who has acted as a principal owner and operator of renewable energy assets for 25+ years.Mr. Kundi is a Mechanical Engineering (BEng Hons), and holds a post graduate Certificate in Business Administration from University of Warwick. He is a Chartered Mechanical Engineer (C Eng) with the IMechE and a Chartered European Engineer (Eur Ing) with FEANI.Mr. Kundi is based in Singapore.






