Fund Summary


Take a long-term, diversified approach to energy investing
 Experience that counts Portfolio Manager David Ginther, CPA, has more than two decades of industry experience and has managed the Fund since inception in 2006. He also has 10 years of international experience with a major oil company. Focus on fundamentals A disciplined process focuses on long-term fundamentals that drive stock performance and investment in long-term secular change. Long-term view The Fund’s long-term approach seeks potential opportunities around the world including demand in developing markets, such as China and India. Current themes include a focus on U.S. shale oil and supporting companies.  




